	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Type `timeleft` in Alfred to see the percentage of the current week, month, quarter, and year that has elapsed and remains, plus days elapsed / total. Press Enter on any row to copy that line; pick "Copy all" to copy all visible lines.

Open Configure Workflow to:
- Toggle each period on or off independently.
- Choose business days (Mon-Fri) or all days per period.
- Optionally set a custom year-end date (e.g. for an annual shutdown).

The year-end date is by-year. Each January it auto-resets to Dec 31, and a reminder appears in the results until you either enter a new date for the current year or clear the field (which means "Dec 31 is fine").</string>
